{"tid":689274,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鬥牛勇士做保鑣　C朗嚇窒恐怖分子","createTime":"2018-06-04T02:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T06:17:21.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"52365e15c5af19782f35d8c841ae168391a257c5","tid":689274,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙巨星C朗為人身安全，決定聘請著名鬥牛勇士Nuno Marecos做私人保鑣，出戰世界盃決賽周。<br />\n<br />\n由於早前恐怖份子組織伊斯蘭國(IS)發布海報，揚言要襲擊今屆世界盃，包括將C朗同美斯斬首，C朗梗係不敢怠慢，精挑細選搵來Nuno Marecos幫手。<br />\n<br />\n身高6尺2寸嘅Nuno Marecos，來頭唔嘢小，除咗係鬥牛勇士之外，亦做過傘兵，同埋參加過綜合格鬥MMA比賽，可以陸空兩棲作戰。佢喺今屆歐聯決賽，亦有負責保護C朗，表現稱職，獲得呢位射手留用。<br />\n<br />\nNuno Marecos平時對付重達半噸嘅公牛，都綽綽有餘，相信等閒之輩，都好難埋到佢身。不過，如果恐怖份子用槍，唔知Nuno Marecos接唔接到子彈呢？"},{"pid":"12fd9a7e07035c2566c64df6d1f2212ae557ee36","tid":689274,"uid":10176,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"收到風王sir就係Nuno Marecos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3816ed4e356890fe839268a68b726e6db42e5bc5","tid":689274,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"一個點夠"},{"pid":"55d2173367c82c34c73ff43c9f1cb1cb1cceb7c3","tid":689274,"uid":90422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"唔請王騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界第一大將軍"},{"pid":"7cba3a8cf052b4fab179f9cb0acb25d6396377fa","tid":689274,"uid":35066,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"55d2173367c82c34c73ff43c9f1cb1cb1cceb7c3","tid":689274,"uid":90422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"唔請王騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界第一大將軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:51:15.000Z","msg":"王騎就係恐怖分子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f122525e22439a7dd10efc69098bc68857a7adc0","tid":689274,"uid":80966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci